HEADWORD: penny-pinching
<hw>penny-pinching</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Extreme care in spending
money; reluctance to spend money unnecessarily.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> parsimony, parsimoniousness, thrift.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

