==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: penny-pinching
<hw>penny-pinching</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Scrimping; reluctant to
spend money; stingy; miserly; same as <er>cheesparing</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> cheeseparing, close.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>penny-wise</ent>⟦br⟧
